## Appendix: Technical Context

<!--
  SECTION: Technical details for reference
  Source: PROJECT.md Constraints + Context

  Keep brief - this is for context, not deep technical discussion
-->

**Stack:** TypeScript, Vercel Functions, Vercel KV, Slack Bolt SDK

**Integrations:**
- **Linear** - Webhook for "QA:Mods" view events, API for user sync
- **Slack** - Events API for message capture, Web API for posting
- **Ceremony Tracker** - Webhook receiver (Phase 7)
- **Grafana** - Alerting webhook (Phase 8)

**What this doesn't replace:**
- Linear's native Slack integration (we reply in threads, not replace)
- Your Playwright test automation (separate repo, you own it)
- Any existing workflows (this adds visibility layer)

